334
00:21:16,318 --> 00:21:17,860
Who am I?
You have your ideals

335
00:21:17,861 --> 00:21:20,363
Like, super-opposite from me, for real

336
00:21:20,364 --> 00:21:21,906
All flaws and empty inside

337
00:21:21,907 --> 00:21:23,616
My Doppelgänger achieved the pinnacle

338
00:21:23,617 --> 00:21:25,326
Only ridiculous common-sense people

339
00:21:25,327 --> 00:21:26,827
Can wear shoes on the dance floor

340
00:21:26,828 --> 00:21:28,579
Going crazy, bombed out,
how's the water temperature?

341
00:21:28,580 --> 00:21:30,039
I can't end here in a city with no future

342
00:21:30,040 --> 00:21:31,582
Technology is a disaster

343
00:21:31,583 --> 00:21:33,251
Keeping people in brilliant anguish

344
00:21:33,252 --> 00:21:36,546
Everyone has their own
"Why? Why?" complex

345
00:21:36,547 --> 00:21:39,799
My title, loser-exclusive,
is high-spec

346
00:21:39,800 --> 00:21:42,927
Neither talented nor with character
Liar, psychopath?

347
00:21:42,928 --> 00:21:46,138
If that's who I am,
I can never be a match for you

348
00:21:46,139 --> 00:21:49,141
Incomprehensible pretty words

349
00:21:49,142 --> 00:21:52,645
I feel awkward with those eyes

350
00:21:52,646 --> 00:21:55,398
They see through my weaknesses

351
00:21:55,399 --> 00:21:58,067
Let me borrow them

352
00:21:58,068 --> 00:21:59,403
Tell me

353
